msgid "GitHub操作示例"
msgstr "Using GitHub"


#: ../../source/collaboration.rst:39
msgid "GitHub是一个流行的Git托管平台，我们可以基于它进行协作。"
msgstr "GitHub is a popular Git hosting platform. We can collaborate upon it."


#: ../../source/collaboration.rst:41
msgid "首先建立一个空的仓库："
msgstr "First, create an empty repository."


#: ../../source/collaboration.rst:47
msgid "进入以下设置界面："
msgstr "Will see this setting page:"


#: ../../source/collaboration.rst:51
msgid "之后用BasicCAT打开一个项目，在项目设置-团队协作里设置远程仓库。"
msgstr "Use BasicCAT to open a project and set the remote repository."


#: ../../source/collaboration.rst:55
msgid "之后将这个项目分发给其它用户即可。"
msgstr "Then, you can package the project to other translators."


#: ../../source/collaboration.rst:57
msgid "其它用户要想修改远程仓库，还需要获得push的权限。"
msgstr "Other translators need to have their own GitHub account and be authorized push permission to the repository."


#: ../../source/collaboration.rst:59
